==English==
===Etymology===
From ''[[south]]'' + ''[[-ward]]''

===Noun===
'''southward'''
#The direction or area lying to the south of a place.

[[category:English nouns]]

===Adjective===
'''southward'''
#Situated or directed towards the south; moving or facing towards the south.

[[category:English adjectives]]

===Adverb===
'''southward'''
